high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter to the right of the oven
Grab the egg off of the counter
Turn around and go to the fridge
Cool the egg in the fridge and then take it out
Turn left and go to the sink
Put the egg in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a cold egg in the sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the sink, then hang a left and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the egg off of the counter.
Walk over to the fridge that is behind you.
Open the fridge door and put the egg inside on the top shelf then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the chilled egg, then close the door.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the sink.
Put the chilled egg into the leftmost sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg in the sink.

high_descs: chill and remove egg from fridge
